channel.title: If You Dont Play Rs Anymore Look Here
channel.description:
Hello if u want to give ur account away, pm me the name and passwords, i am gonna donate them to kids in my school because they all just started, they found out about it from a website that has all the RPG games and i would like you to give them to me so i can give them to them
it would help them out alot. you dont have to if you dont want to, just doing charity work.
